<div class="white-background about-content">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section">
      <h2 class="h4">About this site</h2>
      <p>
        We made this site to provide organizers and engaged residents an
        easier way to learn and share how to give public comment about their
        local police budgets. If you have feedback, thoughts, or questions,
        please get in touch.
      </p>
    </div>
